                </div>
                <div class="mz-l-card-reward-bar col-xs-12">
                    <strong>Earn rewards<sup>2</sup> with every purchase, everywhere</strong> </br>and enjoy special financing.<sup>3</sup>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="col-xs-12 mz-l-card-reward-logo-bar">
                <div class="col-xs-12 mz-l-card-reward-text">rewards run in the family</div>
                <div class="col-xs-12 mz-l-card-reward-logo">
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-6 brand-img">
                        <img src="{% make_url 'cdn' '/cms/files/reward-logo-1.png' %}" alt="reward-logo-1.png">   
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-6 brand-img">
                        <img src="{% make_url 'cdn' '/cms/files/reward-logo-2.png' %}" alt="reward-logo-2.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-6 brand-img">
                        <img src="{% make_url 'cdn' '/cms/files/reward-logo-3.png' %}" alt="reward-logo-3.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-6 brand-img">
                        <img src="{% make_url 'cdn' '/cms/files/reward-logo-4.png' %}" alt="reward-logo-4.png">
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-2 col-xs-12 brand-img">
                        <img src="{% make_url 'cdn' '/cms/files/reward-logo-5.png' %}" alt="reward-logo-5.png"> 
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mz-l-cardholder-bar col-xs-12">
                    <div class="mz-l-cardholder col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                        <a href="https://comenity.net/harmonfacevalues/pub/apply/ApplyIntro.xhtml?cmp=464_web_apply_webbtn"><img src="https://lib.store.yahoo.net/lib/yhst-29523360387793/creditcard-apply.png" alt="Become a cardholder - Apply now"></a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mz-l-cardholder col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-xs-12">
                        <a href="https://comenity.net/harmonfacevalues"><img src="https://lib.store.yahoo.net/lib/yhst-29523360387793/creditcard-manage.png" alt="Already a cardholder? Manage your account"></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="mz-l-creditcard-final-text"> 
