                    5 Qualifying credit cardholders will receive the offer by mail approximately 90 days after meeting the offer requirements. Offer valid in Bed Bath &amp; Beyond, buybuy BABY, Christmas Tree Shops andThat!, Cost Plus World Market, and Harmon Face Values stores, and online at bedbathandbeyond.com, buybuybaby.com and worldmarket.com.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </div>
</div>

